		<title>Do what thou wilt&#8230;</title>
		<link>http://mdk.per.ly/2011/08/07/do-what-thou-wilt/</link>
		<comments>http://mdk.per.ly/2011/08/07/do-what-thou-wilt/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 07 Aug 2011 00:43:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>mdk</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Ironman]]></category>
